@@ -94,0 +94,24 @@
+	<!-- Excluding unused/unread fields for now -->
+	<Match>
+		<Or>
+			<Bug pattern="UUF_UNUSED_FIELD" />
+			<Bug pattern="URF_UNREAD_FIELD" />
+			<Bug pattern="UWF_UNWRITTEN_FIELD" />
+			<Bug pattern="UWF_UNWRITTEN_PUBLIC_OR_PROTECTED_FIELD" />
+			<Bug pattern="UWF_FIELD_NOT_INITIALIZED_IN_CONSTRUCTOR" />
+			<Bug pattern="UWF_NULL_FIELD" />
+			<Bug pattern="NP_UNWRITTEN_FIELD" />
+			<Bug pattern="UUF_UNUSED_PUBLIC_OR_PROTECTED_FIELD" />
+		</Or>
+	</Match>
+
+	<!-- Excluding low level unread public/protected and null-on-some-path -->
+	<Match>
+		<Bug pattern="URF_UNREAD_PUBLIC_OR_PROTECTED_FIELD" />
+		<Rank value="17" />
+	</Match>
+	<Match>
+		<Bug pattern="NP_NULL_ON_SOME_PATH_FROM_RETURN_VALUE" />
+		<Rank value="15" />
+	</Match>
+
@@ -1105,0 +1129,18 @@
+	<!-- Excluding low ranking uncalled private methods for now -->
+	<Match>
+		<Bug pattern="UPM_UNCALLED_PRIVATE_METHOD" />
+		<Rank value="15" />
+	</Match>
+
+	<!-- Seems to be getting it wrong for Medium, e.g. LocalDescriptorProvider$LocalScanner should NOT be static -->
+	<Match>
+		<Bug pattern="SIC_INNER_SHOULD_BE_STATIC" />
+		<Rank value="10" />
+	</Match>
+
+	<!-- These should be properly analyzed - see JMC-8283 -->
+	<Match>
+		<Bug pattern="DE_MIGHT_IGNORE" />
+		<Rank value="10" />
+	</Match>
+
@@ -1291,1 +1333,27 @@
-		
+	<!-- False positives for package lookup in flamegraph color mapper - should be mapped to UNKNOWN_PACKAGE and not be null -->
+	<Match>
+		<Class name="org.openjdk.jmc.flightrecorder.flamegraph.views.FlamegraphSwingView"/>
+		<Method name="createFlameGraph"/>
+		<Bug pattern="NP_NULL_ON_SOME_PATH_FROM_RETURN_VALUE"/>
+	</Match>
+
+	<!-- Store field is used by framework even though it appears unread -->
+	<Match>
+		<Class name="org.openjdk.jmc.ui.celleditors.AttributeEditingSupport"/>
+		<Field name="store"/>
+		<Bug pattern="URF_UNREAD_FIELD"/>
+	</Match>
+
+	<!-- Field is written indirectly through framework -->
+	<Match>
+		<Class name="org.openjdk.jmc.browser.wizards.ConnectionWizardPage"/>
+		<Field name="currentUrl"/>
+		<Bug pattern="NP_UNWRITTEN_FIELD"/>
+	</Match>
+
+	<!-- Equals only checks serverHandle by design since that uniquely identifies an editor input -->
+	<Match>
+		<Class name="org.openjdk.jmc.console.agent.editor.AgentEditorInput"/>
+		<Method name="equals"/>
+		<Bug pattern="EQ_UNUSUAL"/>
+	</Match>
